Don't... Don't do that, Shinya-san! If you do that...

369
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:23,510
Are you okay?

370
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:27,390
Yes, I felt something through my body just now.

371
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:30,270
It's because you're feeling good. You're so cute.

372
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,830
This is...

373
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:38,470
This... This feeling is wonderful.

374
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:42,590
Wow, you're very wet.

375
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:49,470
Shinya-san, I... I...

376
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,670
I'll make you feel much better now.

377
00:24:56,760 --> 00:24:59,550
No, don't look at me.

378
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:03,990
Nope. I want to see all of your body.

379
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:08,350
No. You can't lick a place like that.

380
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:10,710
No!

381
