Narumi-chan, I'm going in.

382
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:24,470
Okay.

383
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:30,390
Does it hurt?

384
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:35,230
I'm fine. Please keep going.

385
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,150
Okay.

386
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:47,110
You shouldn't push yourself.

387
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:50,270
I'm fine! I want to feel you inside me.

388
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:53,950
I want you to fill me up!

389
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:11,350
