394
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,270
Narumi-chan.

395
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:44,870
If you do that, I'm going to feel weird!

396
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:48,990
Narumi-chan, I'm going to...

397
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:52,350
